  27:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****                       ##### DAC Peripheral features #####
  28:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****   ==============================================================================
  29:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****     [..]
