  30:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       *** DAC Channels ***
  31:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       ====================
  32:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****     [..]
  33:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****     STM32F4 devices integrate two 12-bit Digital Analog Converters
  34:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c **** 
  35:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****     The 2 converters (i.e. channel1 & channel2)
  36:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****     can be used independently or simultaneously (dual mode):
  37:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       (#) DAC channel1 with DAC_OUT1 (PA4) as output
  38:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       (#) DAC channel2 with DAC_OUT2 (PA5) as output
  39:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c **** 
  40:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       *** DAC Triggers ***
  41:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       ====================
  42:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****     [..]
  43:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****     Digital to Analog conversion can be non-triggered using DAC_TRIGGER_NONE
  44:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****     and DAC_OUT1/DAC_OUT2 is available once writing to DHRx register.
  45:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****     [..]
  46:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****     Digital to Analog conversion can be triggered by:
  47:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       (#) External event: EXTI Line 9 (any GPIOx_PIN_9) using DAC_TRIGGER_EXT_IT9.
  48:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****           The used pin (GPIOx_PIN_9) must be configured in input mode.
  49:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c **** 
  50:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       (#) Timers TRGO: TIM2, TIM4, TIM5, TIM6, TIM7 and TIM8
  51:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****           (DAC_TRIGGER_T2_TRGO, DAC_TRIGGER_T4_TRGO...)
  52:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c **** 
  53:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       (#) Software using DAC_TRIGGER_SOFTWARE
  54:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c **** 
  55:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       *** DAC Buffer mode feature ***
  56:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       ===============================
  57:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       [..]
  58:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       Each DAC channel integrates an output buffer that can be used to
  59:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       reduce the output impedance, and to drive external loads directly
  60:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       without having to add an external operational amplifier.
  61:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       To enable, the output buffer use
  62:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       sConfig.DAC_OutputBuffer = DAC_OUTPUTBUFFER_ENABLE;
  63:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       [..]
  64:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       (@) Refer to the device datasheet for more details about output
  65:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****           impedance value with and without output buffer.
  66:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c **** 
  67:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        *** DAC wave generation feature ***
  68:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        ===================================
  69:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        [..]
  70:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        Both DAC channels can be used to generate
  71:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****          (#) Noise wave
  72:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****          (#) Triangle wave
  73:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c **** 
  74:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        *** DAC data format ***
  75:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        =======================
  76:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        [..]
  77:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        The DAC data format can be:
  78:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****          (#) 8-bit right alignment using DAC_ALIGN_8B_R
  79:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****          (#) 12-bit left alignment using DAC_ALIGN_12B_L
  80:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****          (#) 12-bit right alignment using DAC_ALIGN_12B_R
  81:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c **** 
  82:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        *** DAC data value to voltage correspondence ***
  83:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        ================================================
  84:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        [..]
  85:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        The analog output voltage on each DAC channel pin is determined
  86:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        by the following equation:
ARM GAS  C:\Users\Administrator\AppData\Local\Temp\cc2oYAmm.s 			page 3


  87:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        [..]
  88:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        DAC_OUTx = VREF+ * DOR / 4095
  89:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        (+) with  DOR is the Data Output Register
  90:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        [..]
  91:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****           VREF+ is the input voltage reference (refer to the device datasheet)
  92:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        [..]
  93:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****         e.g. To set DAC_OUT1 to 0.7V, use
  94:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        (+) Assuming that VREF+ = 3.3V, DAC_OUT1 = (3.3 * 868) / 4095 = 0.7V
  95:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c **** 
  96:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        *** DMA requests ***
  97:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        =====================
  98:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        [..]
  99:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        A DMA request can be generated when an external trigger (but not a software trigger)
 100:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        occurs if DMA1 requests are enabled using HAL_DAC_Start_DMA().
 101:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****        DMA1 requests are mapped as following:
 102:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       (#) DAC channel1 mapped on DMA1 Stream5 channel7 which must be 
 103:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****           already configured
 104:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       (#) DAC channel2 mapped on DMA1 Stream6 channel7 which must be 
 105:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****           already configured
 106:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c **** 
 107:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****      [..]
 108:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****     (@) For Dual mode and specific signal (Triangle and noise) generation please
 109:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****         refer to Extended Features Driver description
 110:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c **** 
 111:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****                       ##### How to use this driver #####
 112:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****   ==============================================================================
 113:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****     [..]
 114:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       (+) DAC APB clock must be enabled to get write access to DAC
 115:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****           registers using HAL_DAC_Init()
 116:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       (+) Configure DAC_OUTx (DAC_OUT1: PA4, DAC_OUT2: PA5) in analog mode.
 117:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       (+) Configure the DAC channel using HAL_DAC_ConfigChannel() function.
 118:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac.c ****       (+) Enable the DAC channel using HAL_DAC_Start() or HAL_DAC_Start_DMA() functions.
